      <section eId="sec_CCP-74-4">
        <num>CCP 74.4</num>
        <heading>74.4. Â Action on an open account or a promissory note</heading>
        <subsection eId="CCP-74-4__subsec_A">
          <num>A.</num>
          <content>
            <p>An action to collect an open account may be brought in the parish where the open account was created or where the services that formed the basis of such open account were performed, or in the parish of the domicile of the debtor.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-74-4__subsec_B">
          <num>B.</num>
          <content>
            <p>An action on a promissory note may be brought in the parish where the promissory note was executed or in the parish of the domicile of the debtor.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=451449</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
